plot: While visiting the US, Vurbmoto had the opportunity to shoot with European phenom Jeffrey Herlings for a 2014 Platinum Edition video. This is the first part of many, so expect much more to come throughout the next few months!
title: Vurb Moto Platinum: Jeffrey Hurlings
